rows.label: qst102105_msg0001
rows.name: So I'm last.

rows.label: qst102105_msg0002
rows.name: You're late! We were sick of waiting!

rows.label: qst102105_msg0003
rows.name: Whoa, take it easy...

rows.label: qst102105_msg0004
rows.name:
I took down five targets.
That's why I'm late.

rows.label: qst102105_msg0005
rows.name:
That's two over the limit, mo!
You ignored the request, mo!

rows.label: qst102105_msg0006
rows.name:
They appeared before
me. I had no choice.

rows.label: qst102105_msg0007
rows.name:
They were the type that would
have caused more trouble if
I'd left them alone.

rows.label: qst102105_msg0008
rows.name: ...Phew, what a relief.

rows.label: qst102105_msg0009
rows.name: What do you mean?

rows.label: qst102105_msg0010
rows.name:
Actually...my weapon was acting up,
so I only managed to take out one.

rows.label: qst102105_msg0011
rows.name:
Is that so, mo? Why didn't
you say anything, mo?

rows.label: qst102105_msg0012
rows.name:
You said you were tired
of waiting... What were
you doing all that time?

rows.label: qst102105_msg0013
rows.name: Oh, shut up...

rows.label: qst102105_msg0014
rows.name:
Besides, what's with the twelve
targets?! Who decided that, anyway?!

rows.label: qst102105_msg0015
rows.name:
Everyone, calm down... Let's
not worry about the details.

rows.label: qst102105_msg0016
rows.name:
Arthem's extra kills covered it,
so the mission is complete.

rows.label: qst102105_msg0017
rows.name:
Nobody says anything, mo! That's
the most troublesome part, mo!

rows.label: qst102105_msg0018
rows.name:
Alright, since we're done,
let's head back and report.

rows.label: qst102105_msg0019
rows.name: Shall we meet there?

rows.label: qst102105_msg0020
rows.name: ...Me too.

rows.label: qst102105_msg0021
rows.name: Bamibami too, mo!

rows.label: qst102105_msg0022
rows.name: What?! O-oh...alright then.

rows.label: qst102105_msg0023
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ] There's no way I can investigate
anything with them like this...
